{"tid":2415511,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"基本（睇你有冇心） 提升性能力的方法","createTime":"2021-02-20T10:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T10:15:35.000Z","uid":265770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"45a7f22fe9447964bcb8928b31e33b312c4850f3","tid":2415511,"uid":265770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:03:04.000Z","msg":"男仔要提升性能力，唔好成日諗d奇怪既方法。其實好簡單，練好臂力、大小腿肌同core，性能力就會提升。<br />\n<br />\n點解？因為如果手臂唔夠力，就算最簡單既全教士，都好快攰，手臂一攰就好快射。<br />\n<br />\ncore 會影響速度。後入大腿小腿要有力。<br />\n<br />\n如果個人真係未練到以上肌肉唔夠力，建議可以將女仔放床邊（前題床夠高），然後男仔企係度，捉住女仔雙腳入，咁就會持久同夠入。如果床唔夠高，可以試台或沙發。或者可以睇下女上男下得唔得。"},{"pid":"3eaab3eb1d2166c98a5d562182e07e1a9caa80e2","tid":2415511,"uid":224533,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:06:41.000Z","msg":"圖中男子應該練咩肌？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9d7zyC2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9d7zyC2.gif&h=a1312ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p.fun48.com/mw690/87417c60ly1ffbp7ev66fg205k05kqsc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.fun48.com%2Fmw690%2F87417c60ly1ffbp7ev66fg205k05kqsc&h=dcb4d090&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ecf71e747984a502483f5922bceac1d9e4a5ce6c","tid":2415511,"uid":265770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3eaab3eb1d2166c98a5d562182e07e1a9caa80e2","tid":2415511,"uid":224533,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:06:41.000Z","msg":"圖中男子應該練咩肌？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9d7zyC2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9d7zyC2.gif&h=a1312ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p.fun48.com/mw690/87417c60ly1ffbp7ev66fg205k05kqsc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.fun48.com%2Fmw690%2F87417c60ly1ffbp7ev66fg205k05kqsc&h=dcb4d090&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:15:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa